name: All Seeing I #14
description: In VR our visual organs (eyes) see one object or one surrounding area, but brain cells perceive and react to that differently. This leads to the confusion of consciousness and the brain, in general. I have conversations with AI using machine learning. Here the GAN is trained on the paintings of the old masters. This series explores the world of emerging tech and the ecstasies of VR. The subject matter is photographed in full VR immersion and then the AI tries to give back the subjects eyes. 1 of
